title: Can we make Jinx's ulti collide with Baron/Dragon?
body: Come on. What's the worst that could happen?

replies.body:
If people are doin' Baron, there still gon' be a boom. It still gon' kill dat Baron.

Regardless, as long as it collides with someone, you can still take it. Same as Ashe arrow. The AOE will kill it if u time it right.
